<h1>Verify your email address</h1>

<p>Hi<%= " #{@user.name}" if @user.name.present? %>,</p>

<p>
  Welcome to Gleania! We're excited to have you on board. To get started, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:
</p>

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <%= link_to "Verify Email Address", @verification_url, class: "email-button" %>
</div>

<p class="text-muted">
  Or copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
  <%= @verification_url %>
</p>

<p class="text-muted">
  This verification link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons.
</p>

<p class="text-muted">
  If you didn't create an account with Gleania, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>

